<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>스티커데이 | Link in Bio</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="네임스티커, 답례품, 문구류 제작과 부업·창업 멘토링을 전하는 스티커데이 링크 모음"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --text: #1f2a54;
        --text-soft: #657199;
        --line: rgba(138, 154, 214, 0.28);
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
        --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(163, 157, 216, 0.18);
        --blue: #86a6ff;
        --mint: #88e7d1;
        --peach: #ffd7ad;
        --lavender: #c7b6ff;
        --yellow: #ffd864;
        --green: #46c47d;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: "Pretendard", "Pretendard Variable", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 2%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), transparent 24%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 0% 18%, rgba(224, 207, 255, 0.7), transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 100% 42%, rgba(198, 242, 255, 0.68), transparent 27%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 78%, rgba(255, 227, 194, 0.72), transparent 25%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f6f2ff 0%, #eef4ff 36%, #fef5ee 100%);
      }

      body::before,
      body::after {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: auto;
        border-radius: 999px;
        pointer-events: none;
        filter: blur(18px);
        z-index: 0;
      }

      body::before {
        width: 15rem;
        height: 15rem;
        top: 8rem;
        left: -4rem;
        background: rgba(219, 202, 255, 0.32);
      }

      body::after {
        width: 17rem;
        height: 17rem;
        right: -5rem;
        bottom: 10rem;
        background: rgba(255, 213, 173, 0.32);
      }

      .page {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: min(100vw, 400px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1.9rem 1rem 2.7rem;
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0.45rem 0 1.45rem;
      }

      .avatar-wrap {
        position: relative;
        width: 6.25rem;
        margin: 0 auto 1rem;
      }

      .avatar-wrap::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -0.28rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7fd6ff, #a48bff);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(141, 153, 255, 0.22);
      }

      .avatar {
        position: relative;
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 1;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 0.3rem solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        background: #fff;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.8125rem, 6.5vw, 2.4125rem);
        line-height: 1.08;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .dot {
        color: #21c7a8;
      }

      .intro {
        margin: 0.62rem auto 0;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        font-size: calc(1rem - 1px);
        line-height: 1.52;
        word-break: keep-all;
      }

      .subcopy {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.45rem;
        margin-top: 0.6rem;
        color: #556284;
        font-size: calc(0.9rem - 1px);
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .subcopy::before {
        content: "";
        width: 0.65rem;
        height: 0.65rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #32d164, #6ae6d1);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(80, 216, 159, 0.14);
      }

      .chips {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.55rem;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 1.1rem;
      }

      .chip {
        padding: 0.62rem 0.86rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(171, 177, 224, 0.12);
        color: #5e678d;
        font-size: calc(0.84rem - 1px);
        font-weight: 500;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 0 0 0.95rem;
        padding-top: 0.85rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(143, 156, 198, 0.22);
        color: #99a0bf;
        font-size: calc(0.88rem - 1px);
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .stack {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.88rem;
      }

      .card {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.85rem;
        padding: 1.16rem 1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        border-radius: 1.6rem;
        background: var(--panel);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        overflow: hidden;
        transition:
          transform 220ms ease,
          box-shadow 220ms ease,
          border-color 220ms ease;
      }

      .card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -30%;
        background:
          linear-gradient(
            118deg,
            transparent 18%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 29%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66) 38%,
            rgba(180, 244, 255, 0.28) 43%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 48%,
            transparent 58%
          );
        transform: translateX(-145%) skewX(-22deg);
        transition: transform 900ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 1px;
        border-radius: inherit;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.34), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12), transparent 44%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .card:hover,
      .card:focus-visible {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(162, 161, 214, 0.22);
        border-color: rgba(165, 181, 241, 0.45);
      }

      .card:hover::before,
      .card:focus-visible::before {
        transform: translateX(145%) skewX(-22deg);
      }

      .card:focus-visible {
        outline: 3px solid rgba(134, 166, 255, 0.28);
        outline-offset: 3px;
      }

      .card.featured {
        padding: 1.32rem 1.05rem;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 15% 15%, rgba(160, 255, 236, 0.28), transparent 26%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(237, 255, 250, 0.84), rgba(239, 248, 255, 0.92));
        border: 1px solid rgba(138, 229, 209, 0.45);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(132, 212, 194, 0.18);
      }

      .card.peach {
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 15% 15%, rgba(255, 241, 200, 0.32), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 249, 239, 0.86), rgba(255, 245, 235, 0.9));
        border-color: rgba(255, 206, 146, 0.42);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(255, 213, 153, 0.16);
      }

      .icon {
        position: relative;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        width: 3.85rem;
        height: 3.85rem;
        border-radius: 1.18rem;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #27836d;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(226, 255, 250, 0.96), rgba(189, 243, 228, 0.92));
        border: 1px solid rgba(101, 225, 194, 0.42);
        box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      }

      .icon.yellow {
        color: #d28700;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 251, 229, 0.98), rgba(255, 233, 157, 0.95));
        border-color: rgba(255, 193, 92, 0.42);
      }

      .icon.blue {
        color: #5a68f3;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(241, 244, 255, 0.98), rgba(205, 216, 255, 0.95));
        border-color: rgba(136, 166, 255, 0.42);
      }

      .icon.purple {
        color: #8b63ff;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248, 244, 255, 0.98), rgba(225, 214, 255, 0.95));
        border-color: rgba(189, 156, 255, 0.42);
      }

      .icon.cyan {
        color: #1491c2;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(233, 252, 255, 0.98), rgba(181, 237, 245, 0.95));
        border-color: rgba(111, 216, 241, 0.42);
      }

      .icon.green {
        color: #18a347;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(238, 255, 242, 0.98), rgba(198, 243, 207, 0.95));
        border-color: rgba(129, 226, 148, 0.42);
      }

      .content {
        min-width: 0;
        flex: 1 1 auto;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.42rem;
        padding: 0.34rem 0.64rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(168, 240, 225, 0.28);
        border: 1px solid rgba(112, 212, 188, 0.28);
        color: #22836f;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .eyebrow::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -30%;
        background:
          linear-gradient(
            120deg,
            transparent 24%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 34%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78) 42%,
            rgba(191, 245, 255, 0.32) 46%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 51%,
            transparent 60%
          );
        transform: translateX(-165%) skewX(-24deg);
        animation: badge-shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .eyebrow.warm {
        background: rgba(255, 214, 156, 0.22);
        border-color: rgba(247, 174, 73, 0.24);
        color: #d27011;
      }

      .title {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.22;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .card:not(.featured):not(.peach) .title {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .desc {
        margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        word-break: keep-all;
      }

      .arrow {
        position: relative;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        color: #a0abc8;
        font-size: 1.28rem;
        line-height: 1;
        font-weight: 300;
        transform: translateX(0);
        transition: transform 220ms ease, color 220ms ease;
      }

      .card:hover .arrow,
      .card:focus-visible .arrow {
        color: #7d8ec3;
        transform: translateX(4px);
      }

      .contact-card {
        padding: 1rem 1.05rem;
      }

      .contact-card .title,
      .contact-card .desc {
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      @keyframes badge-shimmer {
        0%,
        70%,
        100% {
          transform: translateX(-165%) skewX(-24deg);
        }

        22% {
          transform: translateX(165%) skewX(-24deg);
        }
      }

      .footer {
        padding-top: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: #9da5c2;
        font-size: calc(0.82rem - 1px);
      }

      @media (max-width: 420px) {
        .page {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 1.55rem 0.9rem 2.3rem;
        }

        .avatar-wrap {
          width: 5.95rem;
        }

        .chip {
          font-size: calc(0.8rem - 1px);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <section class="hero" aria-label="프로필 소개">
        <div class="avatar-wrap">
          <img class="avatar" src="./assets/profile.png" alt="스티커데이 프로필 사진" />
        </div>
        <h1>스티커데이<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
        <p class="intro">네임스티커 답례품 문구류 제작 및 부업, 창업 멘토</p>
        <div class="subcopy">작은 브랜드의 시작부터 제작 판매까지 함께합니다</div>
        <div class="chips" aria-label="키워드">
          <span class="chip">네임스티커 제작</span>
          <span class="chip">답례품 소량제작</span>
          <span class="chip">부업 · 창업 멘토</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="stack">
          <a
            class="card featured"
            href="https://smartstore.naver.com/stkrday"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <div class="icon">★</div>
            <div class="content">
              <div class="eyebrow">디자이너 출신 대표 브랜드</div>
              <p class="title">스티커데이 스마트스토어</p>
              <p class="desc">나만의 네임스티커, 답례품, 문구류 만들어 드림 / 소량제작가능</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="news-title">
        <h2 class="section-title" id="news-title">상담 & 빠른 연결</h2>
        <div class="stack">
          <a
            class="card peach"
            href="https://pf.kakao.com/_bcFxgG/chat"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <div class="icon yellow">✆</div>
            <div class="content">
              <div class="eyebrow warm">가장 빠른 문의 채널</div>
              <p class="title">카카오톡 채널로 상담하기</p>
              <p class="desc">부담없이 편안하게 물어보세요</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="shop-title">
        <h2 class="section-title" id="shop-title">서비스 & 채널</h2>
        <div class="stack">
          <a
            class="card"
            href="https://idus.kr/Ks3nq"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <div class="icon blue">I</div>
            <div class="content">
              <p class="title">스티커데이 in idus</p>
              <p class="desc">idus 인증 우수작가로 활동중</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>

          <a
            class="card"
            href="https://www.instagram.com/stkr.day/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <div class="icon purple">@</div>
            <div class="content">
              <p class="title">스티커데이 인스타그램</p>
              <p class="desc">모든 활동내역 사진으로 전해 드림</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>

          <a
            class="card"
            href="https://blog.naver.com/stkrday"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <div class="icon green">N</div>
            <div class="content">
              <p class="title">스티커데이 네이버블로그</p>
              <p class="desc">꿀팁이나 소식을 글로 전해 드림</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
        <h2 class="section-title" id="contact-title">메일보내기</h2>
        <div class="stack">
          <a class="card contact-card" href="mailto:stkrday@gmail.com">
            <div class="icon cyan">✉</div>
            <div class="content">
              <p class="title">stkrday@gmail.com</p>
              <p class="desc">더 궁금한 점은 메일로 남겨주세요</p>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="footer">stkrday link page, express your feelings</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
